                        <h3>About</h3>
                        <p>

<u><b>Taskify</b></u> is a reminder application that is not your regular application but an ML-based application. In this application, not only you but your friends, family, and colleagues can set alarms, reminders, and tasks on your phone. Just put in your reminder/task in the text field and our application will sort the task according to its urgency level.
<br> For example, <br>
1. I need to do this task today only.<br>
2. I will do this tomorrow.<br>
Our application will pick up the words (tomorrow,meeting, reminding) and will ask for a confirmation to set a reminder for the meeting.<br>
The 1st task will be sorted on top and frequent reminders will be given on your email id and notification bar on an android device.

